    "title": "Creating a Core Graphics Image from a vImage Buffer"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "vImage provides a function for creating Core Graphics images from vImage buffers. This function allows you to display the results of a vImage operation to your user.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-the-Image",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create the Image",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You create a Core Graphics image from the buffer, and initialize a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/UIKit/UIImage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " instance from that. The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vImage_Buffer/createCGImage(format:flags:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " function returns a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/cgimage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " instance based on the supplied Core Graphics image format (for more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Accelerate/converting-bitmap-data-between-core-graphics-images-and-vimage-buffers",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ").",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following example shows how to create a Core Graphics image from a vImage buffer:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "let result = try? destinationBuffer.createCGImage(format: format)",
            "",
            "if let result = result {",
            "    // Assumes `imageView` is a `UIImageView`",
            "    imageView.image = UIImage(cgImage: result)",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
